"title": "5567: suffering, emotional aspects of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5567",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Suffering gives rise to inner distress, on account of a sense of injustice, frustration, loss or anger.  Christ himself provides an example of such suffering to believers.</p>\n<h2>Causes of emotional suffering</h2>\n<h3>A sense of injustice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:53\">PSA 119:53</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:7\">JOB 19:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps82:2\">PSA 82:2</a></p>\n<h3>Frustration</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:8\">JOB 19:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job23:8-Job23:9\">JOB 23:8–23:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:18\">1TH 2:18</a></p>\n<h3>Loss</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:34\">GEN 27:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:20-Ruth1:21\">RUT 1:20–1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:11-Prov5:14\">PRO 5:11–5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:12\">LAM 1:12</a></p>\n<h3>Bereavement</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:33\">2SA 18:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen23:1-Gen23:2\">GEN 23:1–23:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:34-Gen37:35\">GEN 37:34–37:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:1-Gen50:3\">GEN 50:1–50:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:30\">EXO 12:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut34:8\">DEU 34:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:4\">2SA 19:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:16-Matt2:18\">MAT 2:16–2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:15\">JER 31:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:32-John11:35\">JHN 11:32–11:35</a></p>\n<h3>Childlessness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:1\">GEN 30:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:4-1Sam1:8\">1SA 1:4–1:8</a></p>\n<h3>Parting from loved ones</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:38\">ACT 20:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:41\">1SA 20:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:12\">2KI 2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:6-Song5:8\">SNG 5:6–5:8</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual loss</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:28\">LUK 13:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:4\">JDG 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:11\">MAT 25:11</a></p>\n<h3>Great fear</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:3\">GEN 45:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen20:8\">GEN 20:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:7-Gen32:8\">GEN 32:7–32:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:18-Exod20:19\">EXO 20:18–20:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:24\">1SA 17:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:3-1Kgs19:4\">1KI 19:3–19:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa21:2-Isa21:4\">ISA 21:2–21:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:8-Dan5:9\">DAN 5:8–5:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:26\">LUK 21:26</a></p>\n<h3>Guilt</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:3-Matt27:4\">MAT 27:3–27:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:8\">GEN 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:8\">JHN 16:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:37\">ACT 2:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:2\">HEB 10:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:22\">HEB 10:22</a></p>\n<h2>Emotional suffering in the Lord's work</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's suffering</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:3\">ISA 53:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:38\">MAT 26:38</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:34\">MRK 14:34</a></p>\n<h3>The apostles' suffering</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:28-2Cor11:29\">2CO 11:28–11:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:1-Rom9:4\">ROM 9:1–9:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:31\">1CO 15:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:8-2Cor1:9\">2CO 1:8–1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:19\">GAL 4:19</a></p>\n<h2>Expressions of emotional suffering</h2>\n<h3>Sadness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:1-Neh2:3\">NEH 2:1–2:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:39\">PSA 107:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:3\">PSA 116:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:22\">MAT 26:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:19\">MRK 14:19</a></p>\n<h3>Weeping and groaning</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:1\">JER 9:1</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:24\">GEN 42:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen43:30\">GEN 43:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:1-Gen45:2\">GEN 45:1–45:2</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:30\">2SA 15:30</a> <em>Covering the head and going barefoot were also signs of sorrow</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:12-Ezra3:13\">EZR 3:12–3:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:4\">NEH 1:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:6-Ps6:7\">PSA 6:6–6:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:3-Ps32:4\">PSA 32:3–32:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps137:1\">PSA 137:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa15:5\">ISA 15:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:17\">JER 14:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:75\">MAT 26:75</a> <em>Peter wept bitterly after disowning Jesus Christ</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:35\">JHN 11:35</a></p>\n<h3>Anger</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:1\">JON 4:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:19-Exod32:20\">EXO 32:19–32:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:8\">2SA 6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:10-Rev16:11\">REV 16:10–16:11</a></p>\n<h3>Bitterness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:3\">EXO 17:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam30:6\">1SA 30:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job3:1\">JOB 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:11\">JOB 7:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:3\">JON 4:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:14\">ROM 3:14</a></p>\n<h2>God's response to the emotional suffering of believers</h2>\n<h3>He comforts them</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:3-2Cor1:4\">2CO 1:3–1:4</a></strong></p>\n<h3>He has delivered them through Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:4\">ISA 53:4</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ gives them rest</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:1\">JHN 14:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:28-Matt11:30\">MAT 11:28–11:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:27\">JHN 14:27</a></p>\n<h3>There is no suffering in heaven</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:4\">REV 21:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:10\">ISA 35:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:17\">REV 7:17</a></p>\n<h2>The proper response of believers to emotional suffering</h2>\n<h3>Assessing the problem before God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:16-Ps73:17\">PSA 73:16–73:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:78\">PSA 119:78</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:28\">ROM 8:28</a></p>\n<h3>Controlled emotion before God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg20:23\">JDG 20:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:1-Ps22:2\">PSA 22:1–22:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:8\">PSA 62:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:1\">PSA 74:1</a></p>\n<h3>Prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:7\">HEB 5:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:22-Gen18:25\">GEN 18:22–18:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:9-Gen32:11\">GEN 32:9–32:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:22\">NUM 16:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:15-2Sam12:17\">2SA 12:15–12:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:9\">PSA 38:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps77:1-Ps77:9\">PSA 77:1–77:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah2:1\">JON 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:22-Mark5:23\">MRK 5:22–5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:13\">JAS 5:13</a></p>\n<h3>Continuing to do what is right</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:20-Job1:22\">JOB 1:20–1:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:1\">EPH 4:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:27\">PHP 1:27</a></p>",
